name: Randy McNally
tweet: Grateful for the unanimous and bipartisan support for this resolution. Our thoughts and prayers are with the people of Ukraine as they continue to repel this illegal and immoral invasion.

name: Randy McNally
tweet: Introducing a resolution tonight to urge @POTUS and Congress to expel Putin operatives from our land, ban all Russian imports to America and fully and completely remove Russian banks from our international financial infrastructure. 🇺🇦  #StandWithUkraine   https://t.co/cs3UBJFV6m

name: Randy McNally
tweet: This is quite literally the least we can do. Any economic blowback on our nation can be weathered. We must be clear and unequivocal in our solidarity with Ukraine as they continue to repel Putin’s criminally immoral invasion.

name: Randy McNally
tweet: Only comprehensive economic sanctions can break Putin’s tyrannical hold on power. This includes placing prohibitively high tariffs on all Russian imports or, even better, banning them altogether. Only this will turn Putin’s people against him, hasten his demise and save Ukraine.

name: Randy McNally
tweet: I fully support the removal of Russian banks from the SWIFT international banking system. This removal must be complete and total. Not selected. Not targeted. The West must stand firmly with the heroic Ukrainian people and against the murderous, illegitimate and criminal Putin.

name: Randy McNally
tweet: I am hopeful the Russian people will soon rise up against this authoritarian leader and reclaim freedom for Ukraine and Russia, just as they did in 1991.

name: Randy McNally
tweet: The invasion of Ukraine is an unambiguous war crime. Vladimir Putin is a thug and a criminal. I pray for the people of Ukraine and offer my support as they fight to repel this invasion.  https://t.co/BxU8qCLi5Z
